review.reviewBody: The Crop Dust’n Chippers- Small were a little too salty n the ranch was a bit too milky watery
Awesome wings and everyone should try kamikazee poutine for spicy food lovers.
Got Mighty Dragon, Hot & High and Amelia Earhart. They were all really good and full of flavour.
Great Taste N Top Quality Chicken. Definitely Recommended!!

The wings here are pretty big but juicy and crunchy.I have tried 4-5 different flavours and I had liked all of them but they have 40 more flavours. Do try their dusted fries tossed in mango chipotle its very flavourful
